    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, add the <strong>remaining natural</strong> <strong>yoghurt</strong> and <strong>mayo</strong> to a bowl</p><p>Zest your <strong>lime[s] </strong>(try to grate lightly and avoid grating the white pith, as this is very bitter)</p><p>Peel and finely grate (or chop) your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>chopped garlic </strong>(don't like raw garlic? Go easy!), <strong>lime</strong> <strong>zest</strong> and a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> to the yoghurt – this is your <strong>lime & garlic yoghurt</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-copy-1651599737797-x200.jpg",
